Skill Development Programs
Trugeek design skill development programs based on the industry requirement. The skill development programs enables professionals more productive to meet the challenges of global business competitions by corporates. The course delivery methodology would be innovative, which would include group discussions, brainstorming sessions, practical experiences, case studies etc.

TruGeek design Tailor-made, need-based programs for specific groups or educational streams. These could be, but not limited to:
Soft skills and communications skillsPersonality development and positive thinking skillsLeadership and management skillsInside Sales life cycle and call management skillsMarket Research and Analysis skillsRecruitment training, Aptitude (Arithmetic, Reasoning & Verbal ability) skills
